title: 121: The Walmart Haul Episode: October '20 Edition
itunes:title: The Walmart Haul Episode: October '20 Edition
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa and the gang are trying a wide array of food finds -- fun new flavored waffles, chicken bites that taste like tacos and pizza, an enchilada bake, a new sauce from Heinz, and so much more! Plus, the find of the whole episode… a superfood skillet that is out of this world! So go ahead and push play. Then when you’re done, head on over to the Foodcast page for a list of all the finds mentioned in this podcast!
itunes:summary: It’s time for another Walmart Haul, or as we like to call it… a Haulmart!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
dc:creator: Lisa Lillien
